    "body": "<p>Below are the guidelines for HTML5 ads. If you have HTML5 ads built following the guidelines below, please reach out to your Account Manager or the Customer Delight team to help upload your ads as you currently are not able to do so directly through the dashboard.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">General Requirements</span></strong></p>\r\n<table style=\"cellpadding: 10px;\" border=\"2px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#e5e5e5\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"150px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Zip file requirements and restrictions</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Each individual ad must be its own zip file containing all code and assets (including public, commonly used JavaScript libraries) that make up the HTML5 ad.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">All asset links must correctly reference the file location via its path.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">All assets must be loaded from a secure connection (https).</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Zip file must contain all files referenced from the HTML doc.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">No cross-domain scripting: code references to external domains are not allowed.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">No local storage or session storage libraries allowed.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#f9fcfd\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">HTML doc (index.html file)</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" width=\"400px\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Must be a single, well-structured, and complete HTML document at the root folder</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">HTML tag <strong>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</strong>, <strong>&lt;html&gt;</strong> and <strong>&lt;body&gt;</strong> tags</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Declare the clickTag variable</span></li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Example: <strong>&lt;script type='text/javascript'&gt;var clickTag ='<a href=\"http://www.adroll.com\">http://www.adroll.com</a>';&lt;/script&gt;</strong></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">This clickTag variable must be passed as a parameter to any <em>window.open</em> event inside the ad, usually assigned to the JavaScript onclick event of a div element: <strong>&lt;div id=\"clickArea\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 250px\" onclick=\"window.open(clickTag ,'_blank');\"&gt;</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>&lt;meta&gt;</strong> tags must be used to identify the size of the ad:</span></li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Example: <strong>&lt;meta name=“ad.size” content= “width=300, height=250”&gt;</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Can load into an iframe</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#e5e5e5\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Supported file types</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" width=\"400px\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">HTML, HTM</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CSS</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JS</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">XML</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SVG</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JPG</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JPEG</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">GIF</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PNG</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#f9fcfd\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Supported size</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left wysiwyg-indent1\" width=\"400px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> Maximum <strong>150 KB</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#e5e5e5\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Folder file maximums</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left wysiwyg-indent1\" width=\"400px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> Contains no more than <strong>10 files</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#f9fcfd\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Supported ad sizes</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" width=\"400px\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">728×90</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">300×250</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">160×600</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">300x600</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">468×60</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">120×600</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">336×280</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">250×250</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">320x50</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">970x250</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#e5e5e5\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Supported shared libraries</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" width=\"400px\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Adobe Edge</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http://animate.adobe.com/runtime/6.0.0/edge.6.0.0.min.js\">https://animate.adobe.com/runtime/6.0.0/edge.6.0.0.min.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>CreateJS</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://code.createjs.com/easeljs-0.8.1.min.js\">https://code.createjs.com/easeljs-0.8.1.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://code.createjs.com/movieclip-0.8.1.min.js\">https://code.createjs.com/movieclip-0.8.1.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://code.createjs.com/tweenjs-0.6.1.min.js\">https://code.createjs.com/tweenjs-0.6.1.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://code.createjs.com/soundjs-0.6.1.min.js\">https://code.createjs.com/soundjs-0.6.1.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://code.createjs.com/preloadjs-0.6.1.min.js\">https://code.createjs.com/preloadjs-0.6.1.min.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>JQuery</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js\">https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Angular JS</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.3.15/angular.min.js\">https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.3.15/angular.min.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Tumult Hype</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>HYPE-466.full.min.js</li>\r\n<li>HYPE-466.thin.min.js</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>GSAP</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/TweenLite.min.js\">https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/TweenLite.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/plugins/CSSPlugin.min.js\">https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/plugins/CSSPlugin.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/easing/EasePack.min.js\">https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/easing/EasePack.min.js</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/TweenLite.min.js\">https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.17.0/TweenLite.min.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Swiffy</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://www.gstatic.com/swiffy/v7.3.0/runtime.js\">https://www.gstatic.com/swiffy/v7.3.0/runtime.js</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Additional Notes</span></strong></p>\r\n<table style=\"cellpadding: 10px;\" border=\"2px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#f9fcfd\">\r\n<td class=\" wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"150px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Browser support</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Chrome 40 and above</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Firefox 35 and above</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Internet Explorer 10 and above (including Edge)</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Opera 20 and above</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Safari 7.0 and above</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#e5e5e5\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Supported HTML5 authoring tools</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" width=\"400px\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://creative.adobe.com/products/animate\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Adobe Edge CC</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/flash/how-to/creating-publishing-html5-canvas-document.html\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Adobe Flash CC - HTML5 Canvas document type</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://tumult.com/hype/\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Tumult Hype</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr bgcolor=\"#f9fcfd\">\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-indent1 wysiwyg-text-align-center\" width=\"200px\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\">Supported HTML5 conversion tools</span></td>\r\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left wysiwyg-indent4\" width=\"400px\"><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/swiffy/?hl=en\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Swiffy</span></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>", 
